title: 820-2936 not turning on
message:
Some signs of oxidation in the u2600 region.
Voltage: PPbus_g3h 12.60; pp3v42_g3h 3.43V; PP5v_s0 0v; All_sys 0v; PLt_reset 0v; pp3v_s0 0v

Replaces u2600, but PPVRTC_G3H stands at 0.78V.
